title: Indonesia GDP From Agriculture
description: GDP from Agriculture in Indonesia decreased to 73197.60 IDR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 from 90067.20 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Agriculture in Indonesia averaged 70593.49 IDR Billion from 2010 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 96832.80 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2020 and a record low of 37282.50 IDR Billion in the fourth quarter of 2012. This page provides the latest reported value for - Indonesia Gdp From Agriculture - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Statistics Indonesia
